Dialogs.Dialog: Sleepy... it's impossible not to get sleepy in this season.
This season is kind of warm looking, isn't it？
Hmm, did you see anything spring-like？
What do you know... about spring flowers？
Speaking of spring, cherry blossoms are in bloom, right？ Although they don't bloom for that long.
Speaking of spring... I wonder if it's maybe butterflies.
Spring is, of course, the time for new potato chips！ Right？
Spring is sleep. It's not anytime of the year.
Hot, don't you know that Rinko hates hot weather？
Hey, don't you find it peaceful？ Rinko finds it cute.
When it's this hot, it looks like the air is shimmering, doesn't it？
Somehow, the scenery is also hot... Come on, you can see it too.
Summer means evening showers, sprinkling water... to make it a little cooler.
Summer is all about ice cream.
When it comes to summer, be careful not to suffer from summer fatigue.
Summer... festivals is summer... I'm not so interested in festivals.
It's nice that it's getting cooler. It's a hassle to think about what to wear, though.
I think it is better to go out when it is cooler. It's nonsense to go outside in the heat.
I wish autumn would come next to spring.
The sky is high... what exactly does that mean？
Do you see anything that looks like autumn？
Reds, yellows, and other gaudy autumnal landscapes.
In autumn, you have to make sure you don't fall on fallen leaves.
It's autumn... if it's autumn, we should try some chestnuts.
Autumn, huh... when we were little, we tried to catch dragonflies, didn't we？
Autumn of arts, autumn of music, autumn of Rock n' roll.
It's so cold... I wish they would make it stronger in the cold because I'm not good in the heat.
It's dry and the wind feels like it hurts...
It's not every day that you see a winter scene that is so unique.
Does it get lonely... when you look at the scenery in this season？
I don't mind this feeling of the air being taut... if it were warmer...
Speaking of winter, I can't do without a body warmer, can I？
Winter is all about skiing, and it would be nice if it were easier.
Winter makes me want to eat ice cream in a warm room.
Nekorinko curls up in the kotatsu in winter.
I'm sleepy... I might go to bed indeed.
Waking up early is the best of three worlds... now, what's in it for you？
I rarely go out at this hour, so everything I see is fresh.
As you'd expect, there aren't many people hanging around at this time of the day.
I wonder why the sound of engines at dawn is so resounding.
It's hard to get up, but once you wake up, the morning air might be nice.
Rinko can't have a job that requires her to get up early in the morning. Newspaper delivery, for example.
I wonder. I feel the air is not stagnant at this time of day.
Since we are going out in the morning, we have to enjoy ourselves to make up for it.
After all, no matter what, Rinko is a night owl.
The morning landscape is full of hope... for some reason.
Hmm, I wonder if people who are active at this time are not sleepy.
Based on the tilt of this sun... I wonder what time it is.
Hey, I wonder if the weather will change in the afternoon.
They say you get more done in the morning, but why？ You're just sleepy.
Something that needs to be done in the morning... what was it we？
Well, today is the highest temperature is...
Hey, are you hungry？ Rinko's not bad.
I am sleepy in the daytime. The phrase's an irrefutable truth.
I want to take a nap. I'm sure it would feel good.
Your shadow is short. Why don't you step on it if you can？
Naps during the day. What else is there to do？
Why is there no siesta in this country...
What's the best lunch menu？ Do you have anything like that for yourself？
I hope the snack potato chips... are still good.
Now... what shall we eat for dinner？
Not yet... Rinko's time is at night.
Why is it that evenings always seem so nostalgic to me？
Orange... how do you get such a beautiful color？
Hehe... is Rinko's face sunset-colored, too？
I think it's called "Omagatoki". Can you write it in kanji？
The crows are cawing... I mean, did you sing that when you were little？
I guess it's time for the sun to set...
Hey, do you know what that bird is？ Oh, it's gone...
Finally, it's nighttime. Nocturnal humans will start to be active, just like Rinko.
A date at night... that's what makes it so special.
I have a simple question, why do you have to go home at night？ It's not right, like because my parents tell me to.
Hmm, did you see anything interesting？ Rinko has pretty good night vision.
Oh... I thought I saw something glow, but I think it was my imagination. A cat's eye-like light.
Hmm... I guess it's time to leave, normally.
A couple looking at the night view together... well, sometimes it's nice to be a bit goofy.
Hehe, it's pretty amazing that we can still be together.
Maybe you're sleepy？ Not yet！ ...if you're really sleepy, don't push it, okay？
Hehe, Rinko is not sleepy at all.
Wow, you can see a lot of stars.
It's dark indeed... I feel like I'm being left behind.
Hey, if you're scared, you can stick close to Rinko, okay？
It's so quiet... I feel like shouting out something.
Oh, did something move？ I'm not trying to scare you.
Want some potato chips for dinner？
I can't believe we're together at this hour... nevermind.
I'm not sleepy yet... I can still be up.
Hmm... I think I might be getting sleepy by now.
At this time of day, I'm not sure if you can see anything...
Ah, ghosts！ ...Well, let's just say it's a promise.
Hmm, I wonder how much brighter it will get.
Hey, are you cold？ Rinko, just a little.
This time of day is kind of sharpening my senses... hiya！ I'm kidding.
No one is awake right now except you and Rinko...
Nice weather, isn't it？ A safe greeting series.
Yes, yes. The sun is blessing you and Rinko, too.
It's a beautiful sunny day... are you making teru teru bozu or something？
The sky is so blue, it's youth！
It's cloudy, huh？ It won't affect our date.
I guess I'd rather it be this cloudy.
This makes you feel down. Well, I can't help but feeling depressed.
Clouds are out, I hope it doesn't rain.
When it's cloudy, doesn't it make it ambiguous to know what time it is？
How is a rainy date？ There are many ways to have fun, aren't there？
The floor is slippery on a rainy day... I have to make sure I don't fall.
At this rate... I don't think it's going to stop.
It's raining, raining. I wonder if it will rain until the end of the day.
I didn't think it was going to snow.
If it snows a little, you don't need an umbrella.
Come on, try a funny fall.
Snowy landscape, huh... yeah, not bad.
At this rate... I wonder if there will be snow tomorrow.
Hey, I'm about to get Rinko-fly.
Come on, don't just stand there in a daze. Windbreak, windbreak.
It's windy up there too... See, the clouds are moving fast.
It's windy. Hey... I hope nothing goes flying away.
Lightning. It doesn't fall near you... I hope.
Kya, thunders are scary！ Then, you hug me and get points, okay？
Oh, lightning！ Thunder！ I wanted to say that.
I think I like the moment when lightning strikes. It's like a flash.
This place is a lot of fun. Maybe more than I expected.
This place is nice. A date should be fun, right？
What was the purpose of this place？ What's so fun about it？
Choosing a fun spot is the basis of a date, right？
Hmm, what is it？ Did you find something fun？
Hehe, I'm having fun, don't worry.
Oh, maybe Rinko is the only one having fun？ Come on, enjoy it, too.
Don't worry about Rinko, though, you can have fun.
Come on, you must enjoy it the right way.
Hmmm, if I play at this pace, I might get burnt out.
Heh, whatever, this looks like fun.
It was great to be here with you today.
Everywhere is fun to Rinko if we are together.
Hehe, is that what you think？
Hehe, because, you know, today is fun♪
I feel calm here... like taking our time.
It's a nice place... reassures me.
It's nice and quiet... Nantoka waves are coming out.
I might be too relaxed here.
Sleep...... Oh, no. It's not that I'm bored, it's just that I feel at home.
How are you making yourself at home？ Ojii-chan.
Hmm... seems like it would relieve a lot of stress all at once.
It's like... that soothes the tired modern mind.
I don't know why, but I feel strangely at home.
What makes this so reassuring, the atmosphere？
It's kind of powerful, isn't it？ It calms me down.
I don't know how Rinko can be so calm...
Maybe it's only next to you after all, hehe.
A relaxed date like this might be nice once in a while.
If I settle down too much, I'll get old.
Because, with you, I feel safe everywhere.
Weird sensation... here, I might feel happy.
I understand. I can feel your feelings, too.
I don't know if it's my imagination... but it makes me feel good.
I just wanted to say it. It's okay, not a great deal.
I so want to sleep here, it's so calming.
Hmm... oh, did Rinko just make a loopy face？
For now, forget all your troubles.
You look so relaxed. Were you that tired？
I wonder why this is so calming.
It feels relaxing... where does it hurt？
Hey, do you feel relaxed too？
Even if I have a problem, I can forget it when I do this.
...no, I don't have any worries. For instance.
I wish Rinko could be a part of your healing, you know？
I feel nostalgic... don't you feel like that？
I don't know why this place makes me feel nostalgic.
Just a peace of mind... but it'd be wrong to say that, I don't know why.
I guess this is what it feels like to be... familiar.
This is Rinko-ish, don't you think？
What is this... I don't feel like a stranger.
Why do you think I feel so nostalgic here？
Do you feel nostalgic about this place too？
Hehe, I have a feeling there is something here！
Rinko's prophecy, something is going to happen！
Actually, since a while ago, I've been mysteriously thrilled.
Eh, I wonder if there is something to this...
I'm not sure... I think there might be something there.
There's always something new to discover on every date, isn't there？
What's on the agenda for today...
For dating, you know, it's important to have an attitude of trying to enjoy everything.
I'm not trying to be unreasonable, I just say it's a matter of awareness.
Look at that！ Heh... it's awesome.
Hehe, see what I mean？ Rinko's pretty excited.
If you're having fun too, that's fine.
This place seems to have some interesting anecdotes and stories, doesn't it？
Do you understand？ Rinko is thrilled.
Sometimes it's nice to be excited like a kid.
I want to know everything you care about.
Let's see what's going on here.
What do you want to do？
Hmm, so this is how it is.
What is the point of this？
It may not look like it, but Rinko's having a blast.
You don't have to force yourself to talk, just being together is enough.
There's something about it that's just not right.
What is this？ I don't understand.
This is how you and Rinko are dating.
That's actually based on great odds, isn't it？
It's a little weird, don't you think？
I'm feeling a little restless here...
Doesn't it make you kinda nervous being here？
Is it strange that I'm nervous now？
Or maybe, this kind of feeling is just necessary sometimes.
I don't know, I'm just not comfortable...
Weird place... in a good way.
This is good, isn't it？ Hilarious！
Come on, you can have more fun too, can't you？
With you, Rinko feels like she can laugh a lot.
Being here, doesn't it kind of cheer you up？
Hmm... that's a pleasant place to be.
When I'm on a date like this... I still feel good.
Shall Rinko's energy be shared with you？
Around here... you and Rinko are the best！ I guess.
Rinko is a lucky girl. I'm grateful.
That's what you... no, it's nothing.
I don't mind if we look like an idiot couple.
Our priority is to have fun, not to be affected by how we are seen.
I wonder if this is the right place...
Yeah... I'm actually a little nervous.
You know... I knew it... sorry, I'm still curious.
Are you sure you're okay with this？
I wonder if this is okay...
I'm so happy it scares me！
You know that line, "I'm not a good person". That... might be understandable at times.
You know... can I be next to you？
Hah... I was in a hurry.
I was in a hurry at first...
I can't believe we're supposed to come here together...
This place is kind of... a little scary, I mean...
I have a bad feeling about this...
Because there seems to be something there.
When Rinko says she is afraid, she means...
I'm not afraid. That much is obvious.
With you here, I'll be fine.
Listen, what do you think is ahead？
Well, let's see what's going on.
It would be a waste to just move around.
Well, you don't have to rush to go.
...oh, I'm not keeping quiet because I'm bored... see, you don't even have to force yourself to speak.
Hehe, it's still part of the date.
The way we're doing this... I don't think my siblings can see me doing this.
Just walking around, you know, it's nice.
I wonder if we will eventually have to eat together...
Isn't one of the most important aspects of compatibility the ability to enjoy a meal？
Hmm... Hey, are you buying anything？
How's it going over there？ Did you find anything good？
Since we're here, maybe a souvenir... hmm, now's not a good time.
Hey, which one do you want for Rinko？
Are you buying useless things？ Wasting money is a negative point.
Hey, that. What was that thing？
There is something about specialty food.
I wonder if I can get around all of them.
Do you have any suggestions for sightseeing spots？
Come on, you've been researching, show off your knowledge.
Places you don't know well get you excited, don't they？
I wonder what it would be like to live here.
They say, "Let there be no shame in traveling". Why don't we try a little flirting？
We could go a little more roundabout.
I wonder if there is anything more to this area.
It's still good. Let's look for something.
Hey, did you find anything interesting？
The surrounding landscape could be quite interesting, too.
Let's take a leisurely walk together.
I wonder if there is anything we can play together.
I love the time we spend doing this...
You're never bored, even if you're just walking around.
I'm sure we'll find something eventually.
Hey, hey, do you have anything interesting？
You can also take a gander at the scenery...
Let's talk about something. Anything's fine.
Isn't it a hassle to match your walking speed with Rinko's？
I'm just going to empty my head and go for a walk.
The elements that make a walk enjoyable... I wonder what those are.
Sounds interesting. I hope it's as good as expected.
I hope we can play soon. I don't like to wait.
I wonder if this is interesting. Do you know its reputation？
Hmm, I see. So this is how it feels.
I'm glad we got to play together. Not alone...
I wonder how you and Rinko look to the people around them.
These things, after all, have to be done together.
Enjoy to the fullest～. It's nice to play again.
Wouldn't it be nice to have a little more nature？
Come on, find a place that looks good.
Everyone seems to be busy. Rinko can go at her own pace.
Lemme see... I wonder if it is behaving suspiciously.
There are not many people now... Well, here we go.
It's nice to have a lively atmosphere, but aren't there a lot of people？
The wind feels good. It's by the sea, after all.
...hmm？ Yes, it still smells like the ocean.
Screaming into the ocean... it's not the same as yelling yahoo...
Hey, do you see any interesting boats？
Surprisingly it's a secret spot, it's empty.
As expected, there are a lot of people near the ocean.
Lots of people, everyone loves the ocean...
I feel like the air is clean... Is it because it's by the water？
Look, the view is reflected in the water...
Hmm... I'm still wondering if the air is humid.
Huh？ Did you just splash something on the water？
Hehe, this is a great place.
Huh, not a lot of people... I wonder why.
It's kind of crowded. People, you know, have a habit of gathering near water.
That's a lot of people... Well, okay.
Yes, deep breaths. The air tastes good, doesn't it？
Living in nature... is not what Rinko envisioned, but sometimes it's nice.
If there are no bugs in this...
Being surrounded by nature like this... seems to bring some kind of enlightenment.
It's nice to have so much nature and so few people.
It's nice and empty. It's quiet, undisturbed, yeah...
So many people. I guess that means everyone is hungry for nature.
Now if only I had more room...
This doesn't give you much of a view...
It's a little dark... are you okay？
Wouldn't it be nice to have more light？
Yeah, it's kind of dark and a bit...
It's so dark... can you see Rinko's face？
Let's hold hands. You know, it's dark.
Are you the type of person who cares about UV rays？
The sun is shining, but... I've never cared much about my skin .
Hmm？ Oh, the illumination is strong.
Is it necessary to make it so bright？
I wonder if this would be an easy way to get around.
Hmm, I wonder how far I can go here.
Might seem cramped, don't you think？
I guess I can take a quick look around here.
It's a little cramped, oh well.
Is it oppressive... or is the ceiling too low？
It's like a big open space.
Hey, let's see how far we can go.
You can see it all at once.
Heh, it's a big place inside.
This seems like a lot of work to go around.
I feel good here. I wonder if the ceiling is high.
It's indoors, but it's very open.
Let's take a look around, it looks like a lot of work though.
I can't wait to see where you will take me～.
So, where are we going today？
Well then, let the dating begin！
Of course, you're going to entertain me on today's date.
Where are we going？ Is it a secret？
Actually, you know, I was looking forward to it quite a bit.
Hehe. Didn't you get up early for fun anyway？
If you dawdle, I'll leave you behind.
I know this place has a good reputation... so you have done your research？
Hehe, you wanted to come here. You know what I mean.
Great, I just wanted to visit.
I hear this place is interesting. I've heard good things about it.
I hear this place has a good reputation these days.
I hope we have fun here...
Wow, so this is the kind of choice.
I haven't heard anything about the reputation... but I wonder about this place.
Here again？ You really like it.
Hmm, I don't remember coming here before.
Let's move. I wonder where would be a good place to start...
Okay, let's go to the next place.
Now... shall we take it easy as we move？
Now, I wonder where you will take me next.
...which way do you want to go？
Hmm, from here... I leave it to you.
What's next... hey, what are we gonna do？
Maybe Rinko should decide next. This way is fine.
Hmm, did we go that way earlier, too？ It doesn't matter.
Yes, yes... Huh, is that the same as before？
Hehe, I think it was thanks to my boyfriend's hard work. I've never had so much fun.
This was fun♪ I'm looking forward to the next one.
I had fun today. Let me give you a compliment.
It's been fun thanks to you... hey, are you pushing yourself too hard？
Hey, hey, do you already have a plan for the next date？ Because I had fun today, and I'm curious about the next one.
Hmm... hah... hehe, a sigh of satisfaction.
Aren't you tired？ Well, Rinko feels a little tired.
Yes, it was fun. I look forward to next time.
Today's date was... yeah, it was good.
It's over already... it went by so fast.
Well, it's okay, but... maybe it was just a little bit short, volume-wise.
Huh, is it over？ I see, it was fun.
Yes, it feels like just the right amount of time. I am satisfied.
We've played quite a bit. Any more than that and I'll get a little tired.
In terms of volume, this is about right. A date should be just like this.
I feel like we've had a lot of fun. Aren't you tired？
We had plenty of time to play like this, didn't we？
Maybe it was all about the date. It was a lot of fun.
You know what, maybe we can go somewhere else. Next date, maybe.
Huh, did we go to the same place today as before？ Well, that's okay.
Hey, I found a great date spot... let's go there now.
Now？ Well, it's fine... Okay, I'll get ready, I'll be out in a minute.
Yeah, hey I actually found an interesting date route. Do you want to go now？
Heh... okay. I'll be there as soon as I'm done getting ready.
Listen, I know it's short notice, but do you want to go out now？ I have an interesting date in mind.
Now, huh... okay, I hope it's really interesting.
Leave it to me. I'll see you later.
Actually, you know, I brought a bento.
Don't you think Rinko is amazing for coming prepared even though it was on short notice？
Although I'm a bit upset at the sudden invitation... I actually brought a bento for you.
Right, you should be thanking me.
Ta-da！ I brought a bento. I didn't have much time, but I did my best！
Oh！ I know that was a lot of work, thanks！
